headline: Robinhood Is a ‘Prime Candidate’ for S&P 500 Addition, BofA Says
summary: (Bloomberg) -- Robinhood Markets Inc. is a “prime candidate” to enter the S&P 500 Index in the rebalancing set to be announced Friday, a milestone that would spur passive funds to snap up shares of the online brokerage, according to Bank of America Corp.
